Package: pixelpal
Version: 0.1.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, libgl1, libegl1, libxkbcommon-x11-0, libxcb-cursor0, libxcb-icccm4, libxcb-image0, libxcb-keysyms1, libxcb-randr0, libxcb-render-util0, libxcb-shape0, libxcb-xinerama0
Maintainer: PixelPal contributors <noreply@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/yourname/pixelpal
Description: Layered, cursor-tracking desktop pet overlay
 PixelPal is a lightweight, frameless, always-on-top desktop pet with
 layered cursor-tracking eyes, a reactive mood system driven by real
 system signals, multi-pet awareness, and swappable character packs.
 .
 This package installs the PyInstaller-built onedir bundle to
 /opt/pixelpal and a launcher script to /usr/bin/pixelpal.
